gigabert : a collection of programs to process text files
using Markov(5) chains, with the data stored in a (PostgreSQL) database.

Hubertc: Tokenise text an store the result in the DB.

The tokens are stored
 - as tokens (Duh!)
 - as markov-nodes, referring to the tokens, both forward and backward
 - als posts (articles / documents)
 - as posts_token N:M table
